<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Stylish DevOps Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Global styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        /* Header styles */
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        /* Main content styles */
        .content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Font styles and sizes for different headers */
        h1 {
            color: #ff5733; /* Orange color */
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #4caf50; /* Green color */
            font-size: 32px;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        h3 {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color */
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        h4 {
            color: #e83e8c; /* Pink color */
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        h5 {
            color: #9c27b0; /* Purple color */
            font-size: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        h6 {
            color: #ffc107; /* Yellow color */
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Stylish DevOps Page</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to the World of DevOps</h2>
        <p>This is a stylish webpage that showcases different header styles and font sizes.</p>
        
        <h3>This is a Bold Heading</h3>
        <p>It's important to have clear headings that stand out.</p>
        
        <h4>Subtitles Add Structure</h4>
        <p>Subtitles help organize content and guide readers through the page.</p>
        
        <h5>Important Notes</h5>
        <p>Underlined text draws attention to key points.</p>
        
        <h6>Final Thoughts</h6>
        <p>It's always good to reflect on what we've learned and accomplished.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

